# Start of the game
label intro:

    scene story_1 at pan_zoom with dissolve
    pause 1.0

    show text "Once, in the scorching heat of the far west, there was an army of tireless soldiers, deeply loyal to their country and dedicated to its security. The months under harsh conditions, unpredictable and difficult weather, and at times hunger, not to mention the longing they felt from being separated from their families, shook them to their core." at top_text with dissolve
    $ renpy.pause(4.0)
    hide text with dissolve

    scene story_2 at pan_zoom with dissolve
    pause 1.0

    show text "But most importantly, what truly disturbed the soldiers, wore down their nerves, and sometimes made them willing to take their own lives, was living under the command of someone they feared. Yes, you heard that right. Someone they feared so much they would want to kill themselves..." at center_text with dissolve
    $ renpy.pause(4.0)
    hide text with dissolve

    scene story_3 at pan_zoom with dissolve
    pause 1.0

    show text "This man was a vicious person who considered himself the alpha male of a wolf pack. He was tough, self-centered, and proved his dominance to everyone by demeaning even other men. He was overly confident, strong, masculine, and, in a strange way, incredibly attractive despite all his wickedness." at bottom_text with dissolve
    $ renpy.pause(4.0)
    hide text with dissolve

    scene story_4 
    pause 1.0

    show text "Aside from all these traits, perhaps it was the tension from his high testosterone, which he would do many things to alleviate. In addition to giving his soldiers a hard time, he had subjugated the women in the army just to please himself. The secretaries and nurses in the army would not tell anyone anything because if the word got out, he would be in trouble, and he wouldn't stand for it." at center_text with dissolve
    $ renpy.pause(10.0)
    hide text with dissolve

    scene story_5 at pan_zoom with dissolve
    pause 1.0

    show text "Occasional thirst and hunger made everything even harder for the soldiers. The violent and sometimes humiliating punishments he inflicted on the soldiers were so brutal that no one dared to defy him. All the soldiers in the army had now understood that his word was law here and that resistance was pointless. Sadly, all they could do was accept the situation and continue their days in the army." at bottom_text with dissolve
    $ renpy.pause(10.0)
    hide text with dissolve

    scene story_6 
    pause 1.0

    show text "There were even some rumors circulating in the army. If a soldier wanted extra food and water, they had to be Axel's guest for one night. And when Axel had sex with the nurses, the soldier had to play along with their fantasies." at bottom_text with dissolve
    $ renpy.pause(10.0)
    hide text with dissolve

