    pause 1.0

    show text "The soldiers who were secretly Axel's sex slaves knew this rumor was true because Axel enjoyed all of it. It was even said that some couldn't bear the thirst and found themselves in Axel's room." at bottom_text with dissolve
    $ renpy.pause(10.0)
